metadata.description:
[Bullet] is metaphor about forgiveness, bravery and us

// background();
Each bullet grows up in different backgrounds, they might be pretty and rich in color but also can be pale and poor, like every one of us, bullet cannot choose where it came from and its own past story background. 

// growLogic();
instead of using anger/angst to deal with its life and living with worries, complaints, and fears in the pale past. Bullet chose to understand / organize and extract the best from the past. 

Bullet found the best moments/elements in its past as paints for the future, weave its body and soul with these enhanced colors it picked and turn them into the present self. 

Each bullet are fighting hard to grow/transform and become the best version of itself. 

// A letter to us:
Be brave like this bullet head. 
It swims in the air with no regrets,
and breaks thru all the sonic barriers wall ahead. 

Some bullet's dresses were made up of words. 
Those are the bits I would like to share with every one of us in this room of 256.


'accept your past and everything you owned‚Ä¢',
'do not hate your past as it will not help but only burden your moves',
'from now on you are whoever you want to be',
'they are part of your past but you are all in your future,
'break the thick air wall surrounding you',
'no need to forget, try to forgive',
'Breakthru your future by your past',
'like a bullet, you fly towards your target but not hatred'

